<li class='cover' id='bookCover_222117'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/222117.Writing_Fiction"><img alt="Writing Fiction: A Guide to Narrative Craft" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1266499512l/222117._SX98_.jpg" />
