          </div>
          <div class="stacked" tyle="padding-bottom:15px">
            <span class="readable">&ldquo;I’ve always found that the better the book I’m reading, the smarter I feel, or, at least, the more able I am to imagine that I might, someday, become smarter.&rdquo;</span>
            <nobr>
              &mdash;
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/quotes/497323-i-ve-always-found-that-the-better-the-book-i-m-reading">30 likes</a>
